question_details.resolution_criteria:
This question will resolve as **YES** if the United States Food and Drug Administration approves at least one seasonal influenza vaccine formulation specifically for the 2025-2026 flu season before October 1, 2025.

The question will resolve as **NO** if the FDA does not approve any seasonal influenza vaccine for the 2025-2026 season before October 1, 2025.

Resolution will be based on [credible sources](https://www.metaculus.com/faq/#definitions).&#x20;
